After receiving the telephonic information, all the duty personnel have been alerted and a thorough combing operation has been carried out along with the dog squad. The visitor's entry has already been banned in connection with the Istanbul attack. All preventive measures have been adopted to preclude any possibility of Uniterference to this airport. Any further progress in this acction will be Unitimated. In the wake of high alert situation, extra manpower, has been deployed in the city side. General situation in respect of Chhatrapati Aurangabad airport remains normal. Action Taken: A combing operation & anti-sabotage check of entire Aurangabad airport has been caried out and nothing suspicious found. However, adequate security arrangements have been made to avoid any unwanted  incident.
